translation: Proceed to the next mission?{#Name=" "}
source: Proceed to the next mission?{#Name=" "}

translation: みんなで一つの場所に集まるデモ{#Name=" "}
source: みんなで一つの場所に集まるデモ{#Name=" "}

translation: So this Three chick is another sister of yours?{#Name="Dito"}
source: So this Three chick is another sister of yours?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Unfortunately.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Unfortunately.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Was she this weird when she was young?{LF}Or is that a new thing?{#Name="Dito"}
source: Was she this weird when she was young?{LF}Or is that a new thing?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: No idea. Not my problem.{#Name="Zero"}
source: No idea. Not my problem.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Wow. Now I actually feel sorry for her.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Wow. Now I actually feel sorry for her.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: You know, we haven't seen much of each other lately.{LF}Don't you...miss me?{#Name="Dito"}
source: You know, we haven't seen much of each other lately.{LF}Don't you...miss me?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: ......{#Name="Decadus"}
source: ......{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Hello?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Hello?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh! My apologies, my lady! I did not mean to ignore you.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Oh! My apologies, my lady! I did not mean to ignore you.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: What were you fantasizing about this time?{#Name="Zero"}
source: What were you fantasizing about this time?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: N-Nothing, my lady. Just...thinking about Lady Four. {#Name="Decadus"}
source: N-Nothing, my lady. Just...thinking about Lady Four. {#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Oh? You care enough to remember her, huh?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Oh? You care enough to remember her, huh?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Worry not, my lady. My heart is yours alone.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Worry not, my lady. My heart is yours alone.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: She was acting pretty weird, huh?{#Name="Zero"}
source: She was acting pretty weird, huh?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I assume you mean Lady Three?{#Name="Octa"}
source: I assume you mean Lady Three?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: To be honest, I'm not sure.{LF}She always was a bit of an odd duck.{#Name="Octa"}
source: To be honest, I'm not sure.{LF}She always was a bit of an odd duck.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Though one thing did pique my curiosity...{#Name="Octa"}
source: Though one thing did pique my curiosity...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: What's that?{#Name="Zero"}
source: What's that?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Normally, my love truncheon would rise{LF}to attention at the sight of Lady Three.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Normally, my love truncheon would rise{LF}to attention at the sight of Lady Three.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: But when I beheld her this time, it didn't stir an inch!{#Name="Octa"}
source: But when I beheld her this time, it didn't stir an inch!{#Name="Octa"}

translation: My hat is off to you, Lady Zero,{LF}for taming a lust as voracious as mine!{#Name="Octa"}
source: My hat is off to you, Lady Zero,{LF}for taming a lust as voracious as mine!{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Is that a compliment?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Is that a compliment?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: In any case, Lady Three did leave us with{LF}some rather important words, mmm?{#Name="Octa"}
source: In any case, Lady Three did leave us with{LF}some rather important words, mmm?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: You're awfully quiet. What's wrong?{#Name="Zero"}
source: You're awfully quiet. What's wrong?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Two... Something about that name bothers me.{#Name="Cent"}
source: Two... Something about that name bothers me.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: I often pay scant attention to others.{LF}But something about this Two person just...{#Name="Cent"}
source: I often pay scant attention to others.{LF}But something about this Two person just...{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Is it really that much of a mystery?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Is it really that much of a mystery?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You and Two are supposed to be working together,{LF}after all.{#Name="Zero"}
source: You and Two are supposed to be working together,{LF}after all.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Me? Two? Working? Together?{#Name="Cent"}
source: Me? Two? Working? Together?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Forget it. It's a moot point now, anyway.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Forget it. It's a moot point now, anyway.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Two. Twoooooo...{#Name="Cent"}
source: Two. Twoooooo...{#Name="Cent"}

translation: I sure wish I could be stronger, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I sure wish I could be stronger, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: You and me both.{#Name="Zero"}
source: You and me both.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Do you think I'll ever grow a flower in my eye?{LF}Huh? Do you?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Do you think I'll ever grow a flower in my eye?{LF}Huh? Do you?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: If I had one, I could make it sprout up and blossom,{LF}and then boooooom!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: If I had one, I could make it sprout up and blossom,{LF}and then boooooom!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: This flower ain't all sunshine and lollipops, ya know.{#Name="Zero"}
source: This flower ain't all sunshine and lollipops, ya know.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: And you can't just make it "sprout up," either.{#Name="Zero"}
source: And you can't just make it "sprout up," either.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: First, you need another person to pay for—{#Name="Zero"}
source: First, you need another person to pay for—{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Ah, forget it.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Ah, forget it.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Aw, come on! You can't trail off there!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Aw, come on! You can't trail off there!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: That's mean. You're mean, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: That's mean. You're mean, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: I just wanna be a big, strong dragon!{LF}That's all I want!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I just wanna be a big, strong dragon!{LF}That's all I want!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: So what next?{#Name="Zero"}
source: So what next?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I think Three's right. One might be hiding{LF}somewhere deeper in the forest.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I think Three's right. One might be hiding{LF}somewhere deeper in the forest.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Ugh. I'm so tired of walking through these stupid woods!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Ugh. I'm so tired of walking through these stupid woods!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Well, turning back is just as much of a trek,{LF}so we might as well keep going.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Well, turning back is just as much of a trek,{LF}so we might as well keep going.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Octa speaks the truth. Whether One is here or not,{LF}we should press on.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Octa speaks the truth. Whether One is here or not,{LF}we should press on.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: All right then. Hop to it. {#Name="Zero"}
source: All right then. Hop to it. {#Name="Zero"}
